longBusinessSummary: New Bubbleroom Sweden AB (publ) engages in the online retail of fashion products for women in the Nordic region and rest of Europe. It designs and sells women's clothing, underwear, shoes, and accessories. New Bubbleroom Sweden AB (publ) was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Borås, Sweden.
